ygData.messageBody:
Hiya,

Leshrec and I with another guy name Melfs(non-singaporean), 3 of us went for
hours to Qeynos today.

Oh , I died ..Leshrec too.. LOL. we were near Qeynos and i had to take a
Photo.
A Big Giant by the name of "Choon" came along and hit us bad.
We were bind at Rivervale , so both of us have to go from RiverVale to
Qeynos again. THe 2nd trip was laot faster even thogh we got no SOW this
time round.

It was quite an experience!. i totally enjoy the trip. Melf's spell of
Leviataion is Sooo Cool, when used at HighPass , coming down from those
mountains.nice !

Well, Leshrec and Yutaka, I be in tommorrow morning at around 9:00AM and
log off at 12:30 pm. In at nite at around 8:00pm
Should we get back to Freeport for the meetings (Morning) ?
Let me know your plans? Yutaka , u prepare to re-locate to FP?.

Attached Photos near Qeynos. This the first time i taken shot.. very bad.

btw Lesh, got back me body . 8-)

Laterz

Yiyang at Qeynos
